nd 1934, and the exposure and neglect of over 40 years. Despite the thousands of tourists who visit historic Olvera Street annually, the very knowledge of the mural\'s existence had almost vanished until new interest was generated by plans to have the mural restored several years ago.\" (exerpt)'),(7699,35,2,50,0,'\'America Tropical\': A forgotten Siqueiros mural resurfaces in Los Angeles'),(7704,35,2,40,0,'1932'),(8653,36,2,40,0,'October 8, 2012'),(8652,36,2,45,0,'KCET'),(8650,36,2,39,0,'Jeremy Rosenberg'),(8651,36,2,48,0,'http://www.kcet.org/socal/departures/landofsunshine/laws-that-shaped-la/my-way-or-the-highway-when-mega-roads-took-over-the-city.html'),(468,38,3,74,0,'8'),(469,38,3,75,0,'1'),(470,38,3,77,0,'a:24:{s:8:\"FileName\";s:36:\"be590d7eb8de7a3b80885e148ef31321.jpg\";s:12:\"FileDateTime\";i:1351228946;s:8:\"FileSize\";i:143475;s:8:\"FileType\";i:2;s:8:\"MimeType\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:13:\"SectionsFound\";s:30:\"ANY_TAG, IFD0, THUMBNAIL, EXIF\";s:8:\"COMPUTED\";a:7:{s:4:\"html\";s:24:\"width=\"600\" height=\"529\"\";s:6:\"Height\";i:529;s:5:\"Width\";i:600;s:7:\"IsColor\";i:0;s:17:\"ByteOrderMotorola\";i:0;s:18:\"Thumbnail.FileType\";i:2;s:18:\"Thumbnail.MimeType\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:10:\"ImageWidth\";i:6000;s:11:\"ImageLength\";i:5290;s:13:\"BitsPerSample\";i:8;s:11:\"Compression\";i:1;s:25:\"PhotometricInterpretation\";i:1;s:11:\"Orientation\";i:1;s:15:\"SamplesPerPixel\";i:1;s:11:\"XResolution\";s:4:\"80/1\";s:11:\"YResolution\";s:4:\"80/1\";s:14:\"ResolutionUnit\";i:2;s:8:\"Software\";s:19:\"Adobe Photoshop 7.0\";s:8:\"DateTime\";s:19:\"2012:09:28 12:50:26\";s:16:\"Exif_IFD_Pointer\";i:228;s:9:\"THUMBNAIL\";a:6:{s:11:\"Compression\";i:6;s:11:\"XResolution\";s:4:\"72/1\";s:11:\"YResolution\";s:4:\"72/1\";s:14:\"ResolutionUnit\";i:2;s:21:\"JPEGInterchangeFormat\";i:366;s:27:\"JPEGInterchangeFormatLength\";i:8299;}s:10:\"ColorSpace\";i:65535;s:14:\"ExifImageWidth\";i:600;s:15:\"ExifImageLength\";i:529;}'),(471,38,3,76,0,'FileName:be590d7eb8de7a3b8