 [LCSH]'),(8323,53,2,41,0,'\"Who lives, works, and plays in Downtown Los Angeles? The Downtown Center Business Improvement District (DCBID) conducted the most comprehensive demographic study ever produced in Downtown LA, with over 11,000 responses from Downtown residents, workers and visitors. We use this information to recruit more retailers, restaurants and amenities to our district. Find out everything you ever wanted to know about the demographics of Downtown LA!\" (abstract)'),(8477,43,2,40,0,'2011'),(8483,310,3,75,0,'3'),(8451,106,2,40,0,'2007'),(8445,109,2,40,0,'2012'),(8324,53,2,39,0,'Downtown Center Business Improvement District'),(8325,53,2,48,0,'http://www.downtownla.com/survey/2011/Downtown-LA-Demographic-Study-2011.pdf'),(8326,53,2,45,0,'Downtown Center Business Improvement District'),(8327,53,2,40,0,'2011'),(8328,53,2,37,0,'Downtown Center Business Improvement District'),(1339,74,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1340,75,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1341,76,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1342,77,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1343,78,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1344,80,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1345,81,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1346,82,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1347,83,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1348,84,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1349,85,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1354,86,3,37,0,'Samia Zaidi'),(5757,233,3,74,0,'8'),(1356,88,3,37,0,'Samia Zaidi'),(1357,89,3,37,0,'Samia Zaidi'),(1397,91,3,37,0,'Samia Zaidi'),(8624,51,2,49,0,'Protest movements --United States--History--21st century [LCSH]\r\nOccupy Wall Street (Movement) [LC]'),(1364,58,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1365,59,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1366,60,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1367,61,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1368,62,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1369,63,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1370,65,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1371,66,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1372,67,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1373,64,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1374,68,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1375,69,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1376,70,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1377,71,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(1378,72,3,37,0,'Ryan McGuire'),(13