r in the community, the video remained largely unknown to people outside of LA.\r\n\r\n\r\nDu, charged with murder, got her verdict in October of 1991, a mere 6 months before the Kind verdict came out on April 29. Evading prison, Du was given probation and forced to pay a $500 fine. This verdict, perceived by many in the community as a clear example of the structural injustices faced by Blacks every day, put a deep strain on the relationship between Koreans and Blacks.\r\n(http://www.southcentralhistory.com/la-riots.php)'),(8727,176,2,39,0,'Susan A. Phillips'),(8728,176,2,48,0,'Wallbangin\': Graffiti and Gangs in L.A.'),(8725,176,2,49,0,'Graffiti [LCSH]'),(8726,176,2,41,0,'\"Writer demonstrates his motivation--respect--at the Motor Yard\"'),(8723,177,2,40,0,'1999'),(8720,177,2,39,0,'Susan A. Phillip'),(8721,177,2,48,0,'Wallbangin\': Graffiti and Gangs in L.A.'),(8719,177,2,41,0,'\"Throw-up from NFL, one of the oldest hip-hop crews in Los Angeles.\"'),(8713,178,2,39,0,'Susan A. Phillips'),(8714,178,2,48,0,'Wallbangin\': Graffiti and Gangs in L.A.'),(8712,178,2,41,0,'\"The We Don\'t Care Crips is identified as an enemy in gang writing\"'),(5281,179,2,40,0,'1997'),(5280,179,2,45,0,'University of California, Los Angeles'),(5278,179,2,39,0,'Sojin Kim (Photographer)'),(5279,179,2,48,0,'Vital Signs: Signage, Graffiti, Murals, and \"Sense of Place\" in Los Angeles'),(5275,179,2,50,0,'Gang Graffiti and Known Taggers including \"Chaka\"'),(5276,179,2,49,0,'Graffiti [LC]'),(5277,179,2,41,0,'\"Various types of graffiti, including those of gangs and taggers.  Chaka\'s infamous tag is on the garage door (left)\"'),(8734,175,2,39,0,'Erik Blank (Photographer)'),(8785,152,2,45,0,'University of California, Los Angeles'),(8784,152,2,48,0,'Vital Signs: Signage, Graffiti, Murals, and \"Sense of Place\" in Los Angeles'),(8783,152,2,39,0,'Sojin Kim (Photographer)'),(8780,152,2,50,0,'Graffiti Appropriation on Melrose'),(8781,152,2,49,0,'Signs and signboards [LCSH]'),(8782,152,2,41,0,'\"Gra